# üñ•Ô∏è Freshdesk Ticketing System Project (IT Helpdesk Simulation)

This project simulates a real-world IT Helpdesk environment using the **Freshdesk** ticketing system.
It demonstrates hands-on troubleshooting, user support, and technical documentation ‚Äî all core skills required for IT Support, Cybersecurity, and SOC entry-level roles.

---

## üìå Project Overview
This lab was built to give practical, real-world experience handling IT issues using a structured ticketing workflow.
The project includes:

- 10 fully documented tickets
- Real screenshots of the interface
- A simulated company with users (contacts)
- Documentation of troubleshooting workflows
- Professional ticket notes showing how issues were resolved

This project reflects the type of work done in Tier 1 IT, Service Desk, Jr. Cybersecurity, and SOC positions.

